    window.onresize = function (event) {


        sizeContent();
    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clear();

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

    function sizeContent() {

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

        })

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

        })

sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clear();

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

        }

        }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

    window.onresize = function (event) {


        sizeContent();
    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

        });

    window.onresize = function (event) {


        sizeContent();
    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clear();

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);

        })

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

    function sizeContent() {

            moonBoardObj.resize();

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);

        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {

        }

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

        }

    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }

        }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

    window.onresize = function (event) {


        sizeContent();
    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }

    function sizeContent() {

            moonBoardObj.resize();

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });

    window.onresize = function (event) {


        sizeContent();
    };




    function sizeContent() {
        

        if (moonBoardObj) {
            moonBoardObj.resize();
        }



    }

            function getHoldsetConfig(Id)
        {

             ajax("/Problems/GetHoldsets/" + Id, "GET", null, function (data) {

            moonBoardObj.clearHolds();

            moonBoardObj.clear();

            moonBoardObj.loadHoldsets(data);



            moonBoardObj.renderProblem(problem);


        })
    }



    $(function ($) {


sizeContent();

        moonBoardObj.problemRendered = function (model) {

            var $grdRepeats = $("#grdRepeats").data("kendoGrid");

            $grdRepeats.dataSource.filter({ field: "Id", operator: "eq", value: problem.Id });

        }



        if (problem) {


            getHoldsetConfig(problem.Holdsetup.Id);



        }


        $(".moonTabstrip .closeButton").on("click", function () {

            toggleSlideMenu();

        });




    });
